Name: Fast Jump
About the game: Fast Jump: It is an action game in which you must move quickly to stay alive. Teleport between platforms and shoot all monsters you encounter along the way. Power-ups will help you, as long as you know how to use them. In every mission you will have a boss for you to defeat. Features: Have fun shooting at different monsters ; With an engaging soundtrack , several independent songs; Different missions and bosses that get more and more difficult; Two game modes : Campaign and Adventure; Fun power-ups that will help you defeat the monsters; Multiple characters for you to unlock;
